Removal of Outliers

In [33]:
ub=raw_data.Age.mean()+4.5*raw_data.Age.std()
lb=raw_data.Age.mean()-4.5*raw_data.Age.std()
count=0
for i in raw_data.Age:
    if (i >lb) & (i < ub):
        count=count+1
print(count)
print(raw_data.Age.shape[0]-count)
